author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG and Vive Latino present Live on KEXP from Mexico City with Elis Paprika performing at El Desierto Casa Estudio. Recorded October 17, 2024.

Songs:
Welcome To The World 00:37
Todo Se Está Cayendo 03:31
No Hay Amor 07:57
Now Girls Rule 11:17
Stupid Song 13:55

Elis Paprika - Lead Vocals, Guitar
Cachi Zazueta - Drums, Backup Vocals
Fernanda Nibau - Bass, Backup Vocals
Diez - Guitar, Backup Vocals
Carlos Oceguera Soria - Guitar

Live on KEXP in Mexico City is a partnership with Vive Latino celebrating its 25th anniversary with the support of Indie Rocks! Magazine. Recorded at El Desierto Casa Estudio in Desierto de Los Leones, Mexico.

Host: Cheryl Waters
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Carlos Cruz 

Recorded by Matt Ogaz & JC Vertti
Assistant Engineer: Sebastián Garrido
Audio Mixer: Jon Roberts
Mastered Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Vive Latino Support:
Jordi Puig
Itzel Flores
